 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg>"}]}},{"type":"text","value":"The story","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":4,"offset":1179},"end":{"line":12,"column":13,"offset":1188},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1176},"end":{"line":12,"column":13,"offset":1188},"indent":[]},"data":{"id":"the-story","htmlAttributes":{"id":"the-story"},"hProperties":{"id":"the-story"}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I’ve always wanted to create one of those beautiful ","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1190},"end":{"line":14,"column":53,"offset":1242},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://www.awwwards.com/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"awwwards","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":54,"offset":1243},"end":{"line":14,"column":62,"offset":1251},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":53,"offset":1242},"end":{"line":14,"column":90,"offset":1279},"indent":[]}},{"type":"text","value":" sites you’re probably familiar with. Because it quickly becomes complex to manage what a transition should look like to and from specific sets of pages, I’ve often settled on using a simple fade transition between all pages. It’s complicated and time consuming to set up page transitions and that’s always been a major disappointment for me.","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":90,"offset":1279},"end":{"line":14,"column":432,"offset":1621},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1190},"end":{"line":14,"column":432,"offset":1621},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"I wanted a flexible way to specify when and where a page transition should happen, and only when coming from or going to other specific pages, and I wanted it to be easy to manage that. I wanted the freedom to build anything I could dream up without spending a few hundred hours in the process!","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1623},"end":{"line":16,"column":295,"offset":1917},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1623},"end":{"line":16,"column":295,"offset":1917},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"After hashing it out on a few Gatsby sites I could only find unsatisfactory solutions. First I thought of setting up an object that I could check the current pathname against to derive my transitions from. I almost started building it but the thought of how overwhelming and downright ugly this would be in production stopped me. No thanks! Next, I played with setting transition data on Gatsby templates and pages and then triggering the current page transition based on that data from inside a persistent layout component.","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1919},"end":{"line":18,"column":525,"offset":2443},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":1919},"end":{"line":18,"column":525,"offset":2443},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Though this worked, pages could only have a single exit and entry transition no matter where the user was coming from or going to. This too was not the solution.","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":2445},"end":{"line":20,"column":162,"offset":2606},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":2445},"end":{"line":20,"column":162,"offset":2606},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"After having spent a couple weeks of evenings after work hammering away at this problem, my obsession was still going strong. Laying in bed one night after coding for too long it suddenly hit me: I’ve been looking for a Link between two pages which determines what their shared transition should look like. …a LINK! I had been looking for the simple page link that I’d been staring at and clicking the whole time. In retrospect it’s almost too obvious. Links are already the mediator between pages. They control the default browser page transition (an abrupt jump), of course they should specify which page transition will carry the user from one place to the next.","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":2608},"end":{"line":22,"column":668,"offset":3275},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":2608},"end":{"line":22,"column":668,"offset":3275},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":3,"children":[{"type":"link","url":"#get-started-right-away","title":null,"data":{"hProperties":{"aria-label":"get started right away permalink","class":"anchor"},"hChildren":[{"type":"raw","value":"<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg>"}]}},{"type":"text","value":"Get started right away","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":5,"offset":3281},"end":{"line":24,"column":27,"offset":3303},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":3277},"end":{"line":24,"column":27,"offset":3303},"indent":[]},"data":{"id":"get-started-right-away","htmlAttributes":{"id":"get-started-right-away"},"hProperties":{"id":"get-started-right-away"}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Because I know you might not be as obsessed with creating beautiful page transitions as myself, I created another component called AniLink which wraps around TransitionLink to provide some default transitions. This component offers four transitions; paintDrip, swipe, cover, and fade. Getting started is only a few steps: install TransitionLink, import AniLink to your pages, and set a prop or two to customize.","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":3305},"end":{"line":26,"column":412,"offset":3716},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":3305},"end":{"line":26,"column":412,"offset":3716},"indent":[]}},{"type":"html","lang":"jsx","value":"<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>AniLink</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">fade</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page-2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  Go to Page 2\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>AniLink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":3718},"end":{"line":32,"column":4,"offset":3781},"indent":[1,1,1,1]}},{"type":"html","lang":"jsx","value":"<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>AniLink</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">paintDrip</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">duration</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page-3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  Go to Page 3\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>AniLink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1,"offset":3783},"end":{"line":38,"column":4,"offset":3864},"indent":[1,1,1,1]}},{"type":"html","lang":"jsx","value":"<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>AniLink</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">cover</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">direction</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>up<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">bg</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rebeccapurple<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">to</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page-3<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n  Go to Page 3\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>AniLink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>","position":{"start":{"line":40,"column":1,"offset":3866},"end":{"line":44,"column":4,"offset":3964},"indent":[1,1,1,1]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://transitionlink.tylerbarnes.ca/docs/anilink/","children